data.description: INCREDIBLE PRICE IMPROVEMENT! on this beautiful townhouse with ATTACHED GARAGE near it all in the center of Oak Park location.  ASSUMABLE LOAN for qualified buyers with Interest Rate below 3.25%!  CENTER OF OAK PARK LOCATION -- near it all!--- parks, transportation, shopping,  Ridgeland Commons and OPRF High. The first floor open kitchen/dining leads to the enclosed private patio.    The second level features a bright, comfortable living room, complete with wood burning stove.  Down the hall you'll find the large primary bedroom with two big closets and full bath.   Two additional generous bedrooms, large closets and full bath with laundry are located on the sunny third floor.   New stove and water heater 2023.
